  "summary": "Systems are ultimately driven by human incentives and behavior.",
  "body": "Technology operates inside human systems.\n\nPeople respond to incentives, trust, workload, goals, and social dynamics.\n\nJoz therefore pays close attention to:\n\n- incentives\n- motivation\n- ownership\n- adoption\n- trust\n- organizational culture\n\nThe most elegant technical solution can fail if human behavior is ignored.\n\nSuccessful systems align technology with how people actually work.",
